# Remote Store
IMAPStore        mailbox-remote
Host             mail.mahmoudashraf.dev
Port             993
User             hello
PassCmd          "pass mail.mahmoudashraf.dev"
SSLType          IMAPS
CertificateFile  /etc/ssl/certs/ca-certificates.crt

# Local storage
MaildirStore  mailbox-local
Path          ~/Mail/mailbox/
Inbox         ~/Mail/mailbox/INBOX
Subfolders    Verbatim

Channel     mailbox
Master      :mailbox-remote:
Slave       :mailbox-local:
Create      Both
Expunge     Both
Patterns    *
SyncState   *

